  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t是的，今天是大名鼎鼎的光棍节。一进入十一月，各路人等开始期盼他的到来。</p>\n<p>\n\t不管是街边的咖啡厅酒吧，还是商场里的卖家餐厅，还是各大电商都蠢蠢欲动，意欲宰你一刀。<br />\n\t而无数单身男女在暗自悲叹，有一年一人独自度过。<br />\n\t五花八门，形形色色的光棍节。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t你怎么看，你怎么想。<br />\n\t或者，你打算怎么过？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe Bachelor Day which conveys the best wishes from and to the bachelors at the very beginning has become a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/carnival\" target=\"_blank\">carnival</a> for all the people, not only the owner of the coffee shops, the bars, but also the boss of the restaurants even the sellers on the Internet. However, the only thing I am feeling from this day is the desire to the interests other than the wonderful meaning of the day.</p>\n<p>\n\tActually like what a friend of mine said, If you are single, the Bachelor Day is nothing special compared with the other days; If you are in love, everyday will be the Valentines Day. So, why should us to let the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/greedy\" target=\"_blank\">greedy</a> merchant to make use of this wonderful day?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tToday, everyone wants to get rid of the fate of bachelor and some couples confess in this day. What they forget is that 11th of November is just an ordinary day. A great deal of profits is made in Bachelor day: as we can see in 2011, the margin growth tripled on Taobao. Some traders view it as an excellent opportunity to sell their goods, just as we can see there and here that buy one get one for free on every website. They take advantage of personal psychology of seeking small gains for they think the same goods are much less expensive than usual. Some <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unethical\" target=\"_blank\">unethical</a> business raise price to an extent and cut down it to the original on the bachelor day to cheat buyers so that some consumers purchase numerous inutility goods on this day. From my perspective, I hate Bachelor day because the date remind me of the fact that I will never get a Mr right. Meanwhile, it makes me dizzy on the website because I get choice <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/phobia\" target=\"_blank\">phobia</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/844548/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p566959/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p566959\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p567306/\">奥巴马夫妇被爆婚姻破裂 自拍事件成导火线</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p566826/\">全球地铁无裤日 多国民众脱裤乘地铁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p566950/\">《神探夏洛克》第三季经典台词盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 